Package info.oais.infomodel.implementation

Class InformationPackageRefImpl

java.lang.Object
info.oais.infomodel.implementation.DataObjectRefImpl
info.oais.infomodel.implementation.DigitalObjectRefImpl
info.oais.infomodel.implementation.InformationPackageRefImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
DataObject, DigitalObject, InformationPackage
Direct Known Subclasses:
ArchivalInformationPackageRefImpl
public class InformationPackageRefImpl extends DigitalObjectRefImpl implements InformationPackage
Implementation of an Information Package. This has from the OAIS Information Model
  • InformationObject
  • PackageDescription
  • PackagingInformation
plus additional aspects:
  • Version - which applies to this implementation
  • PackageType - e.g. General or AIP
Author:
david
